con_ge_sted

congested = 擁擠的 / 堵塞的 / （身體）塞住的

直接修飾
Congested roads make me late for work. (擁擠的道路讓我上班遲到。)
間接修飾
The highway is congested because of an accident. (高速公路因為事故而非常擁擠。)


The city center is very congested.
The roads are congested 
I feel congested 
My chest is congested 



I have a congested nose. （我鼻塞了。）
I have a congested chest. （我感到胸悶/痰多。）






⚠️ 小提醒
congested = 形容詞
congestion = 名詞
兩者意思相近，但用法不同
There is a lot of congestion in the city.
The city is very congested.

